  "text": "## Training & Development  \n**New Branch Staff Training:**\n- Banking fundamentals (2 days)\n- Product knowledge (1 day, see [[products]])\n- Customer service (1 day)\n- Compliance & AML (1 day, see [[departments]])\n- Cash handling & security (1 day)\n- Systems training (1 day)  \n**Ongoing Training:**\n- Compliance training (annual)\n- Product updates (quarterly)\n- Customer service coaching (monthly)  \n**See:** Product Training Manual (PTM-001), Branch Operations Training (BOT-001)  \n---",
